A6HtgIOAO2-hwqUY6cEWas09NFf9N_wCbAYeY] the combined market cap of its compa=
nies was $123 billion. Today, the combined market cap of its 17 publicly tr=
aded subsidiaries has nearly doubled to $234 billion, $58 billion higher th=
an Reliance=E2=80=99s market cap.=C2=A0
